  "full_text": "An update for java-1.8.0-openjdk is now available for Red Hat Enterprise Linux 10.\n\nThe RHEL 9.7 GA release was prepared with the most recent release of OpenJDK 8 at that time, which was OpenJDK 8u462, released on July 15 2025. OpenJDK 8u472 was subsequently released on October 21 2025, with existing RHEL 9 releases (9.0, 9.2, 9.4 and 9.6) being updated at that time. This update now brings OpenJDK 8u472 to RHEL 9.7.For more information about the changes in OpenJDK 8u472, see the release notes listed in the References section."
